tariffs and trade 
the 96nation gatt sets rules for international trade and settles 
disputes among its members membership would be a break for 
gorbachev and give the soviet economy greater acceptance within the 
international trading community 
gorbachev is seeking at least observer status he also wants 
membership in the world bank and the international monetary fund 
