im thankful for your understanding and for the fact that you 
did not believe this lie slander this action that evidently was 
directed against me he told cheering supporters in zelinograd 19 
miles northwest of moscow 
just over 1000 people jammed into a hall in zelinograd and 
photographers on the scene said about 20000 more listed to his 
speech on speakers outside 
it was yeltsins first public appearance since he returned from a 
ninecity tour of the united states on monday that same day the 
communist party daily pravda reprinted an article by the italian 
newspaper la repubblica saying the silverhaired populist engaged in 
a drinking and spending binge in the united states 
