at greenwood elementary school scores of 
pupils can count on a free hot meal every day they also can expect 
regular lectures on the evils of drugs both come courtesy of uncle 
sam 
the federal government writes billions of dollars in checks each 
year to educate tens of millions of children across america as is 
the case with most schools greenwoods share goes for everything 
fom lunches to lessons 
the work of the federal government in terms of how it helps 
urban centers is critical said jack taylor superintendent of 
