alameda county superior court 
the settlement came on a civil complaint filed by van de kamp 
that accused itt of assorted deceptions lies and baitandswitch 
tactics 
van de kamp said itt mailed millions of california residents 
invitations to apply for guaranteed loans of 2300 promising 
the money was preapproved with no security required and no credit 
checks 
